OL,1,V]DThe badger arrives at the docking    
OL,2,V]Dplatform. The hover craft service    
OL,3,V]Dlong since discontinued. But now a   
OL,4,V]Dgiant robot crab the size of a car   
OL,5,V]Dferry pulls itself out of the water. 
OL,6,V]DIn large letters the word Sealink.   
OL,7,V]DFor it's 2020 and British rail has   
OL,8,V]Dbeen re-nationalised.                
