OL,3,E figure of John T Bergeraq. Older      
OL,4,E now of course. He is followed closely 
OL,5,E by Antony his conjoined telekinesis   
OL,6,E robot. Antony can also book M.O.T.    
OL,7, Eappointments if needed.               
