OL,2,FThe badger looks into the eyes of his  
OL,3,Fold friend. "You've been away too long.
OL,4,FThe Cyber Mages hold sway on Jersy now 
OL,5,FJames. If you want solve this case     
OL,6,Fyou need join with them, succumb to    
OL,7,Ftheir dark power!"                     
