PN,12509
SC,0009
OL,1,V,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,2,FM UM....WHAT WAS THAT?                 
OL,4,V,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,5,BLast year I heard they were bringing   
OL,6,Bback Bergerac. That's when I conceived 
OL,7,Bthis pitch of what I thought the new   
OL,8,Bversion could be like. I see it as     
OL,9,Bbeing more bladerunnery. With more     
OL,10,Bwizards, robots, talking animals and   
OL,11,Bdangerous cyber cultists. I don't      
OL,12,Bhave any direct insider knowledge.     
OL,13,BBut it's a project whose time has come.
OL,14,BAnd you just get a feel for the        
OL,15,Bdirection fellow artists are going to  
OL,16,Btake! I'll be tuning in to see what    
OL,17,Bmagical surprises the creative team    
OL,18,Bcome up with. I set my version one year
OL,19,Bin the future. now we can see not only 
OL,20,Bhow wrong my predictions for life in   
OL,21,B2020 are but how wrong I am generally. 
OL,22,B                                       
OL,23,BSimon                                  
OL,24,V,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,Fchip-forkV,,,G9/9
